aws:cdk:cloudformation:props.description: Automatically created by the RestApi construct

aws:cdk:cloudformation:props.buildSpec:
version: "1.0"
applications:
  - frontend:
      phases:
        preBuild:
          commands:
            - npm ci
        build:
          commands:
            - npm run build
      artifacts:
        baseDirectory: build
        files:
          - "**/*"
      cache:
        paths:
          - node_modules/**/*
    appRoot: FovusChallenge/client
aws:cdk:cloudformation:props.name: FovusAmplifyApp
